            "title": "本港日間炎熱 市區最高氣溫約28度",
            "description": "<p>天文台表示，一股潮濕的偏南氣流正影響廣東沿岸。本港今早有霧，港內能見度下降至1000米以下。此外，覆蓋沿<br />岸地區的雲帶正逐漸轉薄。</p>\n<p>本港今日料<span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">部</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">分</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">時</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">間</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">有</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">陽</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">光</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">早</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">晚</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">有</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">霧</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">日</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">間</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">炎</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">熱</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">市</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">區</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">最</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">高</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">氣</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">溫</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">約</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">28</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">度</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">新</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">界</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">再</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">高</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">一</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">兩</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">度</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">稍</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">後</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">局</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">部</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">地</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">區</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">有</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">驟</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">雨</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">吹</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">輕</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">微</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">至</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">和</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">緩</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">偏</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">南</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">風</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">稍</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">後</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">離</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">岸</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">風</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">勢</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">清</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">勁</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">。</span></p>\n<p>展望明日日間驟雨較多及有狂風雷暴，下午北風增強，氣溫逐漸下降至周日早上約17度。下周初大致天晴及乾燥，日夜溫差頗大。</p>   </div>\n<p><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/04/11/4052512_ed38b0cdc0d2cae2788fa2baaf2d0470.png\" title=\"\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/04/11/4052512_ed38b0cdc0d2cae2788fa2baaf2d0470_620.png\" border=\"0\"></a></p>\n\t<span class='enlargeImg'><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/04/11/4052512_ed38b0cdc0d2cae2788fa2baaf2d0470.png\" title=\"\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src='https://static.hkej.com/hkej/ejweb/enlarge.gif' align='absmiddle' />放大圖片</a></span>\t\n        ",
            "link": "https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/4052512/%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E6%97%A5%E9%96%93%E7%82%8E%E7%86%B1+%E5%B8%82%E5%8D%80%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%B0%A3%E6%BA%AB%E7%B4%8428%E5%BA%A6",
